						p By stimulating traffic and moderating establishments and events, it will increase demand and most importantly, the reach of visits, encourage the growth in the level and quality of offerings.
				.item.r-card.r-card_check
					span.r-card__header Get the most out of leisure and business events
					.r-card__text 
						p Get the most out of leisure and business events
						p Shuffle is a smart pocket guide that doesn't burden the user, but thinks for them. Sequentially providing a narrow selection of places, events, activities based on: location; mood; interests; weather conditions; budget level, and many other unique features
				.item.r-card.r-card_check
					span.r-card__header Friends and networking everywhere
					.r-card__text 
						p Friends and networking everywhere
						p Shuffle doesn't provoke depression, but breaks it down by considering your emotions. Finding company with similar interests for a specific event or place is not a problem. Finding business events, partners, or communities - however you want
				.item.r-card.r-card_check
